<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>Point Events</h1>
<br>
Welcome to the Point Events index. This page is to record points awarded to users in special cases, e.g. a merchandise purchase. To report a new Point Event, click on "New Point Event". To see the event's details, click show, and to edit it click edit. To move around the website, click "Navigation"
<br>
<br>

<p> My Points: <%= current_user.sum_points %> </p>
<table class="table table-striped">
    <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>User Rank of <%=current_user.counter%> </th>
          <th>First Name</th>
          <th>Last Name</th>          
          <th>Points</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
    <br>
      <tbody>
        <% @count = 0 %>
        <% User.all.sort{|a,b| b.sum_points <=> a.sum_points}.each do |that_user| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= @count += 1 %></td>
            <td><%= that_user.first_name %></td>
            <td><%= that_user.last_name %></td>
            <td><%= that_user.sum_points %></td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      </tbody>
    <br>
</table>
